                  <span class="info-val">
                    B.Eng &amp; M.Eng, Computer Science and Engineering<br/>
                    <span class="uni">University of Aizu, Japan</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="bio">
                I'm a computer science and engineering researcher specializing in computer vision,
                neural radiance fields (NeRF), sim-to-real robotic transfer, and semantic
                communication networks.
              </p>

              <div class="skills-inline">
                <span class="skills-label">Technical Skills</span>
                <div class="skills-badges">
                  <span class="skill-badge lang">Python</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge lang">C++</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge lang">TypeScript</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge lang">Java</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge lang">JavaScript</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge lang">NextJS</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge framework">PyTorch</span>
                  <span class="skill-badge framework">OpenCV</span>
